des:
Alexa and the Orbegozo App products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. 

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you smart devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Orbegozo App products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Orbegozo App" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Orbegozo App account in our "Orbegozo App" app;
(3). You need to have some Orbegozo App devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “Orbegozo App" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Orbegozo App" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Orbegozo App" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Orbegozo App", and you'll be navigated to Orbegozo App login page;
(9). Input your Orbegozo App account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on bathroom heating"
“Alexa, turn off bathroom heating"
“Alexa, set bathroom heating to 45 degrees"
“Alexa, increase bathroom heating"
“Alexa, decrease bathroom heating"
